{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act47side", "eventName": "未許之地", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "UR-7", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "停機坪", "storyInfo": "決心反抗的高登與斯凱一同劫獄救出了娜斯提，但梅蘭德特工早已開始行動。奇怪的是，梅蘭德方引爆浮空層的炸彈後，爆炸的浮空艙卻沒有墜落，而是被萊茵的“樹”牢牢牽住。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "68_g6_floatinglabmodule", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1", "posfrom": "-150,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 0.8}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1", "posfrom": "150,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 0.8}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "第三浮空平台第二次巡邏，目標艙室就位，暫未發現可疑人員。", "name": "特工A"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "除了我們，這個小型浮空平台已經沒有人了，你那邊呢？", "name": "特工A"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "四個艙室的引擎系統都進行了斷點測試，就等園區開進城際網路的覆蓋範圍。", "name": "特工B"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "記得對外統一口徑，將人員聚集到地面是暫時的，直播的展品概覽環節結束後就能返回各自的展區。", "name": "特工A"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明白。", "name": "特工B"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_metalroll", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你確定沒人了？錫人長官強調過，必須確認園區人員全部安全撤離後，才能發送行動訊號。", "name": "特工B"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "主幹通路一小時前已經封死，輔助平台的緊急跳台全部關閉，纜車站的纜車昨晚就改成了單向通行，沒人上得來。", "name": "特工A"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "保險起見……", "name": "特工B"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "100,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……纜車站需要支援，萊茵的那個助理研究員帶著一群體驗員把通行樞紐堵住了，很難纏……", "name": "通訊音"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖，先去支援。計劃的時間點非常重要，一定要趕在直播前完成所有布置。", "name": "特工A"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那剛剛的動靜……", "name": "特工B"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喏，你看。", "name": "特工A"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "汽水瓶蓋？", "name": "特工B"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大概是浮空艙不穩，瓶蓋從桌子上滾下來了。應該沒什麼事，走吧。", "name": "特工A"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walkfast", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walkfast", "volume": 0.8, "delay": 0.3, "channel": "b"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-150,0", "duration": 0.8, "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "posfrom": "100,0", "posto": "-150,0", "duration": 1.2, "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 10.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#10$1", "posfrom": "0,-80", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 0.8}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_2041_1#1$1", "posfrom": "0,-80", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 0.8}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼……雅、雅斯彭先生……", "name": "費爾南"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你到底對那個氣球有什麼執念啊！沙發裡就那點地方，你還要保護氣球，我都快被擠死了！", "name": "費爾南"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_2041_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不好意思，費爾南小姐……但我就是為了這點執念，才求你帶我來這裡的……", "name": "雅斯彭"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從他們眼前開溜，又把你帶過來，真的費了我好大的力氣！", "name": "費爾南"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_2041_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "實在不好意思……能幫我拿一下櫃子裡的工具箱嗎？撤離的通知來得太突然，我來不及確認浮空艙不會在直播裡出現任何問題……", "name": "雅斯彭"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你就那麼想讓“幸運瘤獸”在展覽上亮相？", "name": "費爾南"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不顧聽證會公告的結果，跟一個有多項前科的導遊臨時簽約，還幫她從園區警衛的監視下逃走，只為了讓她帶你回到封鎖的浮空層……", "name": "費爾南"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們這群人啊，對天空真的是太狂熱了！", "name": "費爾南"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_2041_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟我背負的債款是天文數字。只有“幸運瘤獸”在展覽上亮相，吸引投資，我才能有一線生機。", "name": "雅斯彭"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "知道知道，“天空會給所有嚮往未來的人一個答案”嘛，“螺旋槳天堂”的廣告台詞，就連貧民窟的垃圾桶蓋子上都能看到。", "name": "費爾南"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_2041_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就算是盲信，我也走到了這一步，絕不會現在放手。", "name": "雅斯彭"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_guitartap", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_guitartap", "volume": 0.8, "channel": "2", "delay": 0.3}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_2041_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼……元件沒有任何問題，可以撐到展覽結束。走吧。", "name": "雅斯彭"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_doorknob"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "20,0", "duration": 0.3, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "posfrom": "20,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_2041_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "門怎麼鎖起來了？", "name": "雅斯彭"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，你有沒有聽到什麼聲音？", "name": "費爾南"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_devicebeep", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_2041_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽到了……難道我的產品真的出了什麼問題？", "name": "雅斯彭"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不是從展示櫃傳來的，是從——", "name": "費爾南"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們腳下？", "name": "費爾南"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "68_g5_floatingstation", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.05, "yScale": 1.05, "y": 15.0}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖，前面怎麼一動不動啊？再拖下去，直播都要開始了！", "name": "急切的公司代表"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別著急，梅蘭德的人好像過來處理了……有個人被他們圍起來了，看制服款式像是萊茵的研究員？", "name": "好奇的體驗員"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$formal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#12$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請讓我過去！裝置樹的硬碟和主機板還沒拆——", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#12$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "得寸進尺！", "name": "協會成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓裝置樹參與展覽已經是各方能為萊茵做出的最大讓步，而且都大發慈悲允許你們備份數據用於後續研究了，你還想提要求？", "name": "協會成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要五分鐘，我保證不會動任何手腳！管理局的科學顧問不是已經出具了報告嗎？裝置樹並不具備任何危險啊！", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#10$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不行。為了保證展品最終呈現的效果，浮空結構層的所有人員都要前往地面，等開幕致詞結束之後才可以返回。", "name": "協會成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，現在上行纜車全部停運，裝置樹平台又在園區的最高點，你過不去。", "name": "協會成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在看到核心代碼之前，我並不知道娜斯提主任為這項實驗付出了那麼多心血，現在想想，她從來沒有放棄過對天空的夢想……", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪怕只能節省一點點走回頭路的時間，我也想多幫她一些……我必須過去！", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯凱先生，你再胡攪蠻纏，我們只能動用特殊手段了。", "name": "協會成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1", "posfrom": "150,0", "posto": "50,0", "duration": 0.6}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1", "posfrom": "-150,0", "posto": "-50,0", "duration": 0.6}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等……樹好像不太對勁。", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#5$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "十分鐘前你就用過這個說辭了。", "name": "協會成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#5$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1", "focus": "m", "posfrom": "50,0", "posto": "50,0"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1", "focus": "m", "posfrom": "-50,0", "posto": "-50,0"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不不，真的不對！你自己看啊！", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#12$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "BackgroundTween", "attributes": {"yFrom": 15.0, "duration": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "background", "attributes": {"screenadapt": "coverall", "image": "68_g16_sunnyday", "xScale": 1.5, "yScale": 1.5, "y": 30.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "backgroundTween", "attributes": {"duration": 15.0, "yTo": 0.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.3, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "展覽即將開幕，哥倫比亞的陽光也燦爛得應景。順著斯凱手指的方向，眾人看到了那棵熠熠生輝的樹。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "特殊材料包裹著的枝條本應如同陷進松脂裡的小蟲，保持絕對靜滯。然而此刻，在陽光之下，破碎的枝條似乎泛出了……綠意。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1", "focus": "m", "posfrom": "50,0", "posto": "50,0"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1", "focus": "m", "posfrom": "-50,0", "posto": "-50,0"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "68_g5_floatingstation", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有機材料是不可能進行光合作用的……", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "園區手冊上寫得很清楚，展品的外觀在高空環境下發生變化是很正常的事。", "name": "協會成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1", "focus": "m", "posfrom": "50,0", "posto": "50,0"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1", "focus": "m", "posfrom": "-50,0", "posto": "-50,0"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊茵的東西不會。", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不能成為你上去的藉口。", "name": "協會成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1", "focus": "m", "posfrom": "50,0", "posto": "50,0"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1", "focus": "m", "posfrom": "-50,0", "posto": "-50,0"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上去也解決不了問題，我根本不知道它到底是什麼……", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但有一個人一定知道。", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walkfast"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0, "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸，怎麼突然就願意走了？", "name": "協會成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "68_g4_floatingplatform", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……浮空結構層，十一個主平台、二十個輔助平台均已巡查完畢……", "name": "通訊音"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……九個小型浮空艙的發動機內已安裝干擾器和備用引爆器，啟動後這些艙室將依次墜毀……", "name": "通訊音"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……人員疏散完畢，偵察員根據風向和風力反覆估算了墜落曲線，已確認碎片不會影響到人員聚集的廣場……", "name": "通訊音"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2047_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "各區域計劃進展順利，古斯塔夫先生從雲中餐廳的駕駛室發來提醒，“螺旋槳天堂”將於五分鐘後進入特區城際網路覆蓋範圍。", "name": "特工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2047_1#1$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "長官，請指示。", "name": "特工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2047_1#1$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4151_tinman_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有人見到二組的那兩個新人嗎？", "name": "錫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_4151_tinman_1#1$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2047_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "負責轉移那名女妖的？定位顯示，他們現在仍在三號主平台，那裡不在事先規劃的動線範圍內，需要派人去看看嗎？", "name": "特工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2047_1#1$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4151_tinman_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來他們的任務被“接手”了。", "name": "錫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_4151_tinman_1#1$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三號平台離引爆目標很遠，不用擔心，我之後會去解決這個問題。", "name": "錫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_4151_tinman_1#1$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "各組，對時，二階段行動開始。", "name": "錫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_4151_tinman_1#1$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_cellroomB", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$calm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天空被監獄窗口裁成一個狹小的方塊。"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "娜斯提研究的裝置，萊茵最核心的計劃，那棵普通卻神秘的“樹”，此刻被奇裝異服的人影和飛舞的氣球遮掩，不見形跡。"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幾分鐘後，展覽直播即將開始，而一切與娜斯提無關。她身上的骨筆和機械裝置已被盡數收繳，她只需扮演一名無法反抗的罪人。"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "繆爾賽思要是在這裡，說不定會變出八個水分身罵她傻。不過娜斯提並不後悔自己的決定，她只是掛念一個人。"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拂哀菈離開河谷的舉動，始終令她不安，如果有機會……"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_pick_lock", "loop": "true", "channel": "l"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "l", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰？", "name": "娜斯提"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$escape_intro", "key": "$escape_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "娜斯提主任，你必須跟我去裝置樹的平台！", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你應該保管好裝置的資料跟核心代碼，而不是來這裡。", "name": "娜斯提"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但那棵“樹”正在“生長”！", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#12$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……“生長”？不可能。", "name": "娜斯提"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來那不是裝置的常態反應……如果影響到浮空模組，它一定會傷到地面上的人。", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "浮空模組是絕對獨立的，備用電源至少能提供五天的動力，但你所見的異常……只有進入“樹”的內部才能查出原因。", "name": "娜斯提"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快點跟我走吧，主任。", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "監視器被設定了畫面延遲，至少能撐二十分鐘，而且不知道為什麼，牢房的電子鎖也被打開了，趁現在——", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是因為“螺旋槳天堂”的總長官提前幫你開通了權限。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_fsmummy", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4213_skybx_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "f", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "高登？", "name": "斯凱"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"maskid": "ui_cutin_mask_vertical", "style": 1.0, "size": "1280, 250", "offset": "0,200", "channel": 2.0}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 2.0, "type": 2.0, "name": "bg_cellroomB", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "aduration": 0.0, "sfrom": "1,1", "sto": "1,1", "sduration": 0.0}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 2.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "offset": "0,-50", "name": "avg_4213_skybx_1#1$1", "aduration": 0.0, "sfrom": "1.2,1.2", "sto": "1.2,1.2"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 2.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "pfrom": "-15,0", "pto": "15,0", "duration": 5.0}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 2.0, "type": 2.0, "name": "bg_cellroomB", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "aduration": 1.0}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 2.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "aduration": 1.0, "name": "avg_4213_skybx_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"maskid": "ui_cutin_mask_vertical", "style": 1.0, "size": "1280, 250", "offset": "0,20", "channel": 3.0}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 2.0, "name": "bg_cellroomB", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "aduration": 0.0, "sfrom": "1,1", "sto": "1,1", "sduration": 0.0}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "offset": "0,-50", "name": "avg_4213_skybx_1#1$1", "aduration": 0.0, "sfrom": "1.2,1.2", "sto": "1.2,1.2"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "pfrom": "15,0", "pto": "-15,0", "duration": 5.0}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 2.0, "name": "bg_cellroomB", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "aduration": 1.0}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "aduration": 1.0, "name": "avg_4213_skybx_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你……身上的那些是什麼啊？手工製作的高空面罩、改裝螺旋槳，還有二手的隔熱太空服？", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#5$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 2.0, "clear": "true"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "clear": "true"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是去洗劫了園區的資源回收場嗎？", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#9$1"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4213_skybx_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_4213_skybx_1#1$1"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽證會上你顛倒黑白的證詞還貼在園區的布告欄上，現在主動幫我們越獄……總不能是你良心發現了吧？", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#10$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4213_skybx_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "娜斯提，被收繳的骨筆和機械裝置我都帶來了。聽證會的事，抱歉。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_4213_skybx_1#1$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比起表演那個人準備好的稿子，我寧願跟你一起站在被告席上——好歹那些被收繳的裝置確實是我的貨物，我該為此承擔罪責。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_4213_skybx_1#1$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你真的是高登·譚農？", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#12$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "發生了什麼事？", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_broadcast_third"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特區市民及收看展覽直播的觀眾們，非常榮幸能為大家介紹，即將成為哥倫比亞歷史上重要里程碑的實驗園區——“螺旋槳天堂”！", "name": "園區廣播"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4213_skybx_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的時間不多了。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_4213_skybx_1#1$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "娜斯提，你跟古斯塔夫做過交易，應當不會懷疑我接下來要說的秘密。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_4213_skybx_1#1$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的老上司在跟梅蘭德計劃著什麼，對嗎？", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4213_skybx_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你比我想像的還要敏銳。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_4213_skybx_1#1$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有三十分鐘就要致詞的園區總長官出現在這裡，就是最好的證明。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "市民朋友們，請你們望向窗外的天空。再動人的宣傳詞也比不上親眼所見，雲層之下的未來景致正在等待你們瞻望！", "name": "園區廣播"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4213_skybx_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們想用一場事故終止展覽，斷送“螺旋槳天堂”的未來，但我並不清楚他們的詳細計劃。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_4213_skybx_1#7$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果梅蘭德參與其中，他們動手的速度會很快。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 5.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_explo_n", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼聲音！", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#5$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天啊，是我眼花了嗎？浮空結構層有什麼東西正在下墜——那是“幸運瘤獸”的浮空艙？！", "name": "園區廣播"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#5$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不只這樣……三個、四個……這是開幕儀式的一環嗎？稿子裡怎麼沒寫？要是真的掉下來了——", "name": "園區廣播"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#5$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等！艙室好像停止墜落了？彷彿有什麼東西牢牢拉住了它們……", "name": "園區廣播"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#5$1"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，負責人你說什麼？哦、哦，看來各家科技公司都準備了很多驚喜，連我也差點被騙了！", "name": "園區廣播"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#5$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不需要任何學術論文和數據證明，螢幕前的觀眾們都親眼看到了“螺旋槳天堂”在浮空領域的突破，而這僅僅是展覽的開始！", "name": "園區廣播"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#5$1"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不可能，哪怕是正在研究的計劃中，也沒有一款急停模組可以做到這種程度……", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯凱，你的實地測算比較精準，下墜的浮空艙本來應該掉落在哪裡？", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "憑肉眼估算，浮空艙墜落時很可能會砸毀二號主平台，把連接上下層的主通道堵死——", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是通往裝置樹平台的唯一路徑。", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#9$1"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "高登，我接受你剛剛的道歉，但我無暇參與你的計劃。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4213_skybx_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛剛發生的奇蹟絕不是一時好運，它或許與你以及你的發明有關？", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_4213_skybx_1#1$1"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是威脅？", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4213_skybx_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是我對所有“違規”事物的直覺性判斷。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_4213_skybx_1#1$1"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對付古斯塔夫這種小事根本用不著你幫忙，但我需要一個能在塵埃落定之後保住整個“螺旋槳天堂”的籌碼。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_4213_skybx_1#1$1"}, {"id": 368, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的裝置樹……", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#5$1"}, {"id": 370, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4213_skybx_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓你去處理只有你知道的事，就是我計劃的一部分。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_4213_skybx_1#1$1"}, {"id": 372, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我明白了，萊茵的人會配合你。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1"}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是高登，無論你打算做什麼，一旦有危險立刻向裝置樹靠攏，我會接應你。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.5, "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "150,0"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4213_skybx_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_4213_skybx_1#4$1"}, {"id": 382, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4213_skybx_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "零五四，東西都準備好了嗎？", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_4213_skybx_1#1$1"}, {"id": 384, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2040_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "準備好了。", "name": "太空鱗獸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2040_1#1$1"}, {"id": 386, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4213_skybx_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走吧，快到開幕致詞的時間了。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_4213_skybx_1#1$1"}, {"id": 388, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "hidecgitem", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}